{
  "id": "expert-emojf",
  "title": "emojf",
  "description": "Create a 2D interactive graph visualization featuring a week-based timeline and emoji trajectory mechanics. The scene includes a text title, a line graph with days of the week as X-axis labels, and vertical dotted lines marking each day. Users initiate recording to activate a moving emoji dot that cycles through various emojis based on Y-axis input values. The dot travels horizontally with random vertical vectors, leaving behind emoji markers when passing each dotted day line. The final result displays 7 emojis connected by line segments, creating a visual trajectory across the weekly graph. The game may include Y-axis input controls, emoji selection systems, line styling options, and animation effects for smooth transitions between points. [source: emojf.json]",
